Name: Gravity Finance
Description: Gravity Finance is DeFi platform deployed on the Polygon Network and currently offers the following features: Swap Exchange; Farms; Yield Optimizing; Vaults; Launchpad (token sales).Gravity Token Holders (GFI) earn fees from the platform’s products and are also entitled to various other benefits.The official Gravity Finance ticker is “GFI” and trades under that name on all the exchanges where it has been listed. The designation “GRAVITYF” is for CryptoCompare.com only.Discord | Medium
